==========
[directives/macro] macro definition with percent (%) prefix
==========
.macro foo %bar %baz
---

(program
  (directive
    mnemonic: (macro_mnemonic)
    name: (macro_name)
    parameters: (macro_parameters
      (macro_parameter)
      (macro_parameter))))

